profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

We specialize in designing homes, drafting the necessary construction drawings and then filing for the required building permits. 
This includes designing for new buildings, removal of a load-bearing wall, renovations, additions, garages, deck, basement conversions into suites and single-family home conversions into legal duplexes. 
We also provide client support and representation where a minor variance is required by the Committee of Adjustment. 
Do you have an upcoming construction project on your mind? 
Contact us today and we can offer you some helpful tips for getting started.

Fine Finishes Design Inc. is a premier design and decorating firm serving the Greater Toronto area since 1997. 

We have a well earned reputation for attention to detail and professionalism in residential and commercial design.  Fine Finishes Design Inc. works closely with their clients and places special emphasis on understanding their unique needs, tastes and budget.  
Andrea Colman, the Principal Designer and Creative Director of Fine Finishes Design Inc. oversees each project personally ensuring the highest quality service.

Andrea graduated with the highest honours in the CIDC Design Program and is considered to be one of the best designers in the greater Toronto area.

Andrea is one of the founding members of The Benjamin Moore Painting and Decorating Services in North America and has sat on the Advisory Council for Benjamin Moore’s Painting and Decorating Services Canada.

With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources, and craftsman that exceed client expectations.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling cost control and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

Modular Home Additions has developed a revolutionary concept using sophisticated computer software and building techniques. In just days, a second storey addition or new home, custom designed to your needs, can be built. All structural building parts are designed and built in a climate controlled environment. This enables us to have a high quality level and build all year round without leaving your house vulnerable to weather conditions. There is minimal noise, dust and no mess.
Combining technology with excellent service, achieving your dreams is easier, faster and affordable. Using factory built components can save you up to 30% compared to conventional methods. And best of all, you are able to stay in your home during renovations without being inconvenienced. Our accurate quotation software ensures no hidden costs. This one-stop approach to renovating is a wise choice amongst many alternatives and gives you the optimum value for your home.

profile:
We have been providing our construction services for almost 15 years helping our clients to renovate and enhance their living space. Novacon Construction Inc are a full DESIGN-BUILD firm focusing on large scale higher end Major renovations, Home additions and full Custom Homes. We are a very well planned company that work well with clients that are looking for a high end/professional building experience and not a jack of all trades approach. Our clients work with a professional DESIGN-BUILD team that consists of in house designer, Project manager, Site supervisor and tradesman for the duration of their build.
 
Our aim is to produce a high quality product, to perform in the most efficient way possible, and to make your renovation a positive and rewarding experience. All our trades people are highly skilled and bring with them a wealth of experience. NOVACON Custom Builders & Renovators are equipped to work on any area of your home, from major additions, basements, to bathrooms, including kitchen development and we can even build your dream home!
 
A satisfied customer is our best advertisement!!!.

profile:
CHC is the Canadian exclusive dealer for Patio Enclosures Products Proudly serving Ontario and not limited to Toronto, Surrounding GTA and Tri-Cites areas.
Patio Enclosures has been building and creating beautiful living spaces since 1966. We have had the opportunity to transform many dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market.

This dedication and care has made Patio Enclosures the largest manufacturer and installer of Sunrooms, Solariums and Conservatories in the industry. As an award winning company, we take great pride in every new room or addition we produce. Patio Enclosures products are distributed to  branches, franchises and dealers to provide you quick service at a competitive price.

All of our Sunrooms, Solariums, Additions and Conservatories are designed and custom-manufactured in our factory. As a NARI certified remodeler, we work to make sure every product you receive from Patio Enclosures is the best quality and fit for your home. If your design requires special attention, one of our engineers will work closely with you to create and design a Sunroom, Solarium, Traditional Addition or Conservatory that works with your home, lifestyle and budget.

profile:
"My Prestigious Home" is where you need to be...

MPH has been a leader in major renovations and custom home construction since 2007. From concept to completion, we take a client’s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project and better to say, your investment. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, MPH is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our vast professional experience, skilled expertise and attention to details enable us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. That’s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way.
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.

We understand custom homes and renovations are amongst the most important investment to people in their lifetime. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that MPH is most definitely the qualified team for your project.

We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally hundreds of renovations since our inception. 

Please view our website at http://MyPrestigiousHome.com to view images of some of our projects.

Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship.

With 2 year Warranty, we at MPH know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients.

Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

MPH is an innovative, full service design/build/construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There are many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands.

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our company’s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones.

Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free. Remember, we are talking about Professional Advice from Skilled Engineer.
Our areas of servings are in Toronto, Beaches, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Richmond hill, Markham, Foresthill, Royal York, Vaughan, Woodbridge, East York, West end, Central Toronto, North York, & Downtown Toronto.

"My Prestigious Home"
Impact on Community, Providing Quality

TC Homes is proud to work with the highly experienced architects and designers of this industry.

TC Homes has two main purposes: to bring quality and safety to life and to exceed customers’ expectations by building every element to perfection.

TC Homes Contracting has provided diverse services for clients and architects throughout the GTA region for more than 20 years. As a full service contractor, we have the skills and experience to manage, build and support a wide variety of project types and client needs; we strive to provide excellent services …

services:
At any scale, TC Homes presents each client with superior service and attention throughout the project. 

Services include:

new construction 
renovation/tenant improvements 
project management 
construction management 
bobcat excavation
estimating and scheduling 
in-house services 
renovations 
From beginning to end, effective construction management is essential to any project. The Project Manager coordinates all aspects of the project and is the primary contact for all needs and concerns for the duration of the project. TC Homes has a commitment to the project and team and employs pre-construction value engineering, savings through negotiated projects, and project-specific construction strategy, while presenting and maintaining the construction schedule with expert project coordination.
The In-House Service Division provides TC Homes clients with continued service after construction is complete. This includes:

facilities management 
monthly or yearly inspections 
cost analysis for budgets 
hourly rates for in-house work 
third party negotiations for other services 
24-hour emergency service 
commercial painting 
exotic coatings 
occupied painting

profile:
QUALITY IS A WAY OF LIFE:

Inputting over 20 years of experience into the field of construction, Artycon has become recognized as one of the leading Custom Construction Firm. Innovative techniques, customized planning, and impeccable service have allowed us to skyrocket to success and maintain a strong and loyal clientele.We have the passion for creating and building your dream project. We care about maximum efficiency and love to see satisfied client. 

Our Strategy: 

Providing authentic and mindful construction plan along with 100% customized design for each client has been and always will be the number one priority for Artycon Custom Construction . A commitment to extensive documentation and archiving of past projects, along with progressive sourcing and implementation allows us to be exceptional in providing client with top of the experience.

Why Choose US: 

We Love What We Do-
We have the passion for creating and building your dream project. We care about maximum efficiency and love to see satisfied client.

We Truly Care-
The right care can ensure the success of any projects. We believe in partnership & trust and work with you to create a great space. 

Our Promise to You-
We have an unwavering philosophy of caring for our project and our customer's perspectives in order to accomplish the best quality project to grantee your satisfaction. 

Trust-
Our relationship with our clients, professional partners, and subcontractors has transparency. With complete honesty from the start, there is a neutral base to work from. Our foundation is to build a trusting relationship, leading to many successful endeavors together.  

Our Team-

Over the years, we have built solid relationships within the construction industry and our team are highly competent to provide professional services to our customer and clients in the industry from architects, interior designers to specialized trades like Concrete worker, Carpenter, Dry-Waller, Taper/Plasterer, Electricians, Plumbers, HVAC, Painter, Landscapers etc. We are confident these working relationships have helped us to provide our customers with the best quality services for your projects.

We are fully insured and we make sure to use the right procedures to protect you and your property. 

Additionally, we strive to maintain a clean job site and will take necessary steps to keep disruptions to you and your home to a minimum. 

Call us today, and see what our commitment to quality is all about! We may not be related, but you’ll feel like we’re family.

profile:
Established in 1998, by husband and wife team Gerry and Lindsey Anacleto, Anacleto Design quickly became an award winning design firm with accolades both locally and internationally.
now in our 16th year in business we have been fortunate to work with extraordinary clients in both commercial and residential design. Our experience in both commercial and residential design has provided our design savvy clientele with unique and timeless design solutions. We pride ourselves on our personalized approach to our work and often build a personal relationship with our clients that lasts long after the project is completed.
In 2008, we also founded “Homes by Anacleto Design”, our sister company, which oversees the design, construction and project management of our residential work. Design-build is literally what we do; we purchase land, research and assess the potential of the site, design the project accordingly, build it and sell it. We offer this “One Stop Shop” experience for our clients as well who are seeking a hip, urban design which is paired successfully with old world craftsmanship. With three new complete house projects booked thus far for “2014”, it is proving to be another exciting year of growth and success for both companies. 
We welcome you to visit our website at www.anacletodesign.com and follow us on Facebook as well for regular updates!

profile:
Chi-Noodin Sustainable Renovations applies a holistic approach to renovations, offering design + build for homes with sustainability in mind.
Mission - A Sustainable Proposition
Jeff and his team will work with you to reduce the environmental impact of your project by applying the right design philosophy, materials, equipment and construction methods while enhancing your comfort levels and reducing your energy bills.
Description
Chi-Noodin stands for "Big Wind". It is Jeff's Anishnawbe spirit name, "Big Wind that brings change to the people" It is this name that has given him the inspiration to apply a holistic approach to renovations, offering design + build for homes with sustainability in mind.

The Brief
Any given project is about the people and their story. Jeff will sit and listen carefully to this story and develop a design brief prior to creating physical plans. This will ensure that the end result matches the owner's requirements.

The Team
The client is central to any project team. Jeff will liaise directly with you throughout your project. He will assemble a team of professionals to suit the needs of the project. He will coordinate all efforts and be your single point of contact from start to finish.

Services
Depending on your location Jeff can provide all professional services within his team or work with your preferred local realtor, architect, engineer and licensed trades people. As a LEED Accredited Professional, Jeff will ensure that your project meets and exceeds the current building standards.

Great Value
By offering both design and build services, Jeff will be there to monitor progress from day one until the project is handed over to you, the client. With his architectural background he understands the intricacies of the multitude of disciplines involved and with his hands on construction experience he knows what it takes to really get the job done well. Jeff will be able to quote your project accurately and guarantee an excellent end result.

A Sustainable Proposition
Jeff and his team will work with you to reduce the environmental impact of your project by applying the right design philosophy, materials, equipment and construction methods while enhancing your comfort levels and reducing your energy bills.

Corell Homes is a Tarion-Registered Toronto Custom Home Builder. We believe that constructing a home should be a fun and memorable experience - not a stressful one! That is why our Fixed-Price and 200-Day Guarantees have become so popular. Simply put, we will lock-in your cost of building, and guarantee your home to be built within 200 days!

profile:
We build beautiful modern homes of all shapes and sizes.
From heritage properties, condominiums, to new builds, we love reinventing and transforming contemporary spaces for design enthusiasts. We provide both design and construction services catered to our client’s needs. From ideation to filling your space with everything it needs, we provide a seamless full service to our clients.

HIGH QUALITY CRAFTMANSHIP
Contemporary is clean and simple. We have a passion for refinement of materiality and detailing. That is why we work with an extensive network of professionals who exceed expectations instead of managing them.

PROJECT MANAGEMENT
We believe in creating positive attitudes with our project team members and our clients. When we’re excited about your project, it inspires others to be excited about it as well.

MODERN DESIGN
We love to observe human interaction with light, space and objects. Through collaboration we discover dynamic multidisciplinary solutions to everyday and, sometimes, mundane space.

WE LOVE TO BUILD
Archetype Construction has over 20 years experience in the construction and design industry. We believe in fostering great relationships with trade contractors, suppliers and retailers, consultants, designers – and especially our client. Being transparent and honest is what we know to be indispensable in our relationships with our clients. This is what separates us from most, and what our clients respect most about us. Based in design and innovation, we approach all residential projects with the appropriate sensitivities to detail, quality, and budgets

Check out my latest projects here:
https://www.instagram.com/archetypeconstruction/

profile:
BROOKVIEW FINE DECKS 

BUILD YOUR DREAM DECK OR BRING YOUR OLD WEATHERED DECK BACK TO LIFE! 

With over 20 years of Custom Deck Building experience, we offer a free comprehensive deck assessment whether building from scratch or restoring your weather beaten deck. 

We supply new deck quotes with custom drawings and the ability to change dimensions when required. 

We also offer deck repair and refinishing for those of you that just want to bring your deck back to it's original finish. A complete pressure washing with an environmentally friendly cleaning agent is applied and all dirt, grime, stain and mildew is removed. A light sanding to prepare the wood to accept the stain follows. After that, you are free to pick the color of your choice. All of this can be done in approximately 2 - 4 days. We will work within your schedule. 

Need a fence, gazebo or pergola built or restored? We will accommodate. 

CALL NOW FOR A FREE ESTIMATE! 
Office: 647-922-1853 

We service Toronto, Scarborough, Brampton, Etobicoke, Oshawa, Whitby, Ajax, Pickering, Mississauga, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Thornhill, King City, Markham, Aurora and Newmarket. 

Office Hours: 
Monday: 7am - 9pm 
Tuesday: 7am - 9pm 
Wednesday: 7am - 9pm 
Thursday: 7am - 9pm 
Friday: 7am - 9pm 
Saturday: 9am - 5pm 
Sunday: 9am - 5pm 

Estimates within 1 hour outside our service area will be billed $50.
